Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:54.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い事　揺れる音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:57.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そっとひそめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:05.11,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}頬のそばで舞う雪達…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:12.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}たくさんの後悔　過去を結ぶ笑顔たち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:15.44,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風のささやき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:18.56,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}触れて溶ける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:26.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冬空の淋しさを重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:34.95,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}優しさの瞳越えて　今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:42.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伝えたいメロディ　指差した一番星光る空に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:50.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描き集めた未来　かじかんだ指の隙間通る星座たち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:58.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Ah　この場所から見た景色　叶えたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:04.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約束ね
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:54.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中的愿望  摇曳的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:57.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悄悄隐藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:05.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}让飞雪滑过脸颊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:12.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}挥之不去的后悔  紧系过去的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:15.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北风的细语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:18.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一触即散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:26.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寒空中夹杂着寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:34.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}越过了眼中的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:42.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}现在想给你的旋律  遥指着初星的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:50.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}天空拼凑出的未来  手指间露出的星座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:58.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊  想要实现在此看见的景色…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:04.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}约定好了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:51.89,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}長い間積もっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:58.72,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}すれ違いに気付いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:09.40,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}だからその想いを救える場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:16.58,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}置きに行こう　今ならできるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:25.30,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}淡い記憶辿りながら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:30.40,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}糸と糸たぐり寄せていつか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:33.40,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}僕らは出会う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:43.30,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}幼い願い満ち溢れ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:59.66,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}奇跡を起こすの　この町に　ah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:10.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}無邪気に君と笑うあの日と変わらない時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:21.16,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ふと手を伸ばせばそこに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:48.66,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}白く光る星のカケラ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:53.82,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}それは心の奥刻まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:56.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}淡いぬくもり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:23:06.73,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}幼い過ちさえほら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:24.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}触れたら溶けてく雪のように
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:51.89,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}长时间的积累
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:58.72,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}察觉到擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:09.40,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}所以将思念带往救赎之地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:16.58,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}安放在那里  现在一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:25.30,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}随着谈谈记忆的到达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:30.40,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}线与线终将会交织在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:33.40,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我们相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:43.30,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}小小的愿望得以满足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:59.66,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在这个小镇  降临奇迹  ah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:10.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}与你天真的笑容一样不变的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:21.16,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}忽而把手伸向那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:48.66,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}星星的碎片闪耀着白光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:53.82,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}那是刻在心灵深处的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:56.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}点点温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:23:06.73,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就连儿时的那些过错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:24.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}也仿佛雪花一样渐渐消融
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽先生  你的脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春  不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽先生  怪兽先生他生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生病？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别介意  反正已经很旧了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近正想着要换一个新的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发啰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思  还要特意过来接我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.56,0:00:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.63,0:01:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.51,0:01:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  诺艾尔也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  诺艾尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  一起来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也邀请过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.71,0:01:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是被拒绝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔要和怪兽先生在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.38,0:01:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽…先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽先生
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:15.92,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,460)\pos(395,270)}「我所失去的东西」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是谢谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮了我们这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点小事不要在意  上班顺路而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装什么帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我们去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点儿  快点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不坐一会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下多可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次来这边  不好好玩一下怎么行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初三学生都没有时间可以好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北美祭的演出节目也还没有决定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香没有准备什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小时候一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这么说来  小春也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小时候比起来没什么变化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候开始  就照顾着柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家里面也是最成熟的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这样呢  我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  看上去成熟是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我戴上的话也会一样变得成熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去看风景了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好东西要留到最后再去看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是诺艾尔和汐音也能一起来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户川同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  没有跟你说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我邀请了汐音  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那天我有安排了  很多年前就约好了的」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是委婉地拒绝了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟不是直率的人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不疼  不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼死啦  疼死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子疼得快要死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:05:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽先生  不要死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了  千万不能死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要激动  不要激动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦  刚才是我在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为诺艾尔  怪兽先生他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  才不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑而已  开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是小小开了一个玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好知道啦  我也会帮怪兽先生治病的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已经走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是什么都没有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在这种地方等上一个小时？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道  可是不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说过要好好享受这里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个跟这个说的才不是一个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有个地方能坐坐就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还带着这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着这是吃便当的必备用品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是刚好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  看我的看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是店里最有人气的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来不是自己做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做倒是妈妈做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它们弄得这么好看的可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦  知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前好像也有过像这样大家一起分着吃便当的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天文台？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是只有小春忘记带便当了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是乃乃香拜托大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来大家把便当放在一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来乃乃香也是干劲十足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果最后变成我吃到了最豪华的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  乃乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  有心事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恋爱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  我们吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽先生会好起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么担心它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙也会感到欣慰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有诺艾尔帮得上忙的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么帮我按着它的手臂  让它别乱动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不跟着小春她们一起出门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们叫上你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太远了  看不到飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话不就只能待在这附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  帮我好好按住它吧  诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「走吧」算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一句话就把我给打发了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连乃乃香也这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这里也太大了  要走多久才到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我估计差不多快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向没有错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸给了我地图
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地图？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\move(440,100,427,107)\bord0\1c505050\fs16\t(\fs15)\frz-3}这里！\N第四行\N从右数第6个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找这个目标建筑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给爸爸打个电话  确认一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个的话  刚刚已经看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香你什么都不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交给她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没有错的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了确认一下  我们再走一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话怪兽先生就会好起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有疼痛的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然太马虎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  再进行一次手术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定没错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果因为柚季  我们才迷路了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在先别理我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去打水  你休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有心事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我们是硬跟着过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是回避一下的比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我一直很害怕见到妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想现在也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没有和大家说想见妈妈一面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许就不会来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我只看过照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你妈妈看起来很温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她非常温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常温柔  总是笑容满面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是抱着我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖洋洋的  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握着的手却总是冷冰冰的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7年前  从小镇离开后不久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才知道搬家是为了妈妈的治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果  妈妈还是走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我十分悲伤  感到很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得所有事物都变得漆黑一片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那时候  我就不想再回忆起往事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的声音和笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妈妈一起生活过的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就没有发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数次  无数次的和自己说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  真的变得不再痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心不再疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  和大家的珍贵记忆也一同消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季也是  小春也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑太也是  诺艾尔也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还伤害了汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你已经记起来我们的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈一定不会原谅我做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会认为我是她值得骄傲的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许从一开始  就没有这样认为过也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么乃乃香会在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  你是过来见你妈妈的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你是下定了决心去面对她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我和凑太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.95,0:14:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香的话没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…绝对没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不容许任何反驳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从天文台那时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香就是值得我骄傲的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  能不能再等会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再给我一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先过去等你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到这个季节了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像星星一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪下得好大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  汐音？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是汐音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  汐音你最后还是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像从前那样说说话如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  刚才汐音…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚大家在湖边集合看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音见过乃乃香的妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我们成为朋友创造契机的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心想和她成为朋友的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就笑得更灿烂些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说不要这样愁眉苦脸的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记忆中的乃乃香也一直都是笑容满面的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈也一定想看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的乃乃香的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽先生在高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  它现在一定在感谢诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说「我好高兴」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且小春也不用伤心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春不会去买新的怪兽先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小春说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这只雾龙对她来说是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是这么喜欢这只雾龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想要拜托柚季和凑太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季画出形态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我切割木板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后和小春三人一起上色完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家一起做出来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香那时的笑容  不知给过我多少次勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说这一定是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香一直都很珍视妈妈说的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  挺起胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多快见到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉  没能去看你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年就拜托给乃乃香了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫古宫乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我成为朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是爸爸的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说今年因为工作原因不能来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了答谢凑太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和凑太有好好努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然确实和原来有点不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽先生  恢复健康了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.59,0:21:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实呢  或许这样也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}我都说可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}因为我可是看板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.43,0:21:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}流星雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}嗯  虽然还要再等几天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}到时能看见很多流星从夜空中划过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}小汐音也来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}好美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}流星雨还要更闪耀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}嗯  到那时我们一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.95,0:22:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}星星也在看着你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}像是在微笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.73,0:22:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}一定是因为你们也在笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}汐音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.69,0:23:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}汐音让我转告你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}曾想和你一起去看流星雨的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}曾想和她一起去看流星雨的
